  "text": "Appropriate homogenization is crucial and minimizes the risk to draw a nonrepresentative sample and was recently also emphasized by Garcia-Lara [CITATION_1] . However, we feel that the recommendations given by the manufacturers are not sufficient and need to be modified (see also Figs. 5 and 6).",
